            <lg xml:id="TK1320">
<l>niṉaittiruntu nōkkiṉuṅ kāyu maṉaittunīr</l>
<l>yāruḷḷi nōkkiṉī reṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even when I look on her contemplating (her beauty), she is displeased and says, "With whose thought have you (thus) looked on my person?"</l>
            </lg>
